# .gitignore — generated by fabricdeploy.
# This directory is a standalone deploy estate, meant to live in its OWN git
# repository (separate from your fabric.yaml). These entries keep it small:
# `terraform init` downloads provider binaries into .terraform/ that can be ~1GB+.

# ---- Terraform: local state & downloaded providers (never commit) ----
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
*.tfvars.local
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# .terraform.lock.hcl IS intentionally committed — it pins provider versions
# for reproducible deploys. Do not add it here.

# ---- Secrets / local config (never commit) ----
.env
.env.*
*.env
secrets/
*.pem
*.key

# ---- Editor / OS noise ----
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
